      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661731\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrAOVLight</a> is a handy utility light that allows a lighting artist to output a shot-specific AOV mask without needing to request one from the shading artists or generate a <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662011\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19662011\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662011</a> (LPE).</p><h3 id=\"AOVLight-LightLinkingwithPxrAovLight\">Light Linking with PxrAovLight</h3><p>Use <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544645013/Light+Linking\" rel=\"nofollow\">Light Linking</a> to include/exclude pieces of geometry in the AOV. In this example, the PxrAovLight is &quot;off&quot; globally and &quot;on&quot; the tree in the scene.  This linking set up creates creates a mask of the tree.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"485\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=485&amp;height=485\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645211/aovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645231\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"aovLight_primary.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645211\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"83b6ac96-f26b-405d-95d7-ffa57c315904\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=485&amp;height=485 1x\"></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"485\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_mask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=485&amp;height=485\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645211/aovLight_mask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645234\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"aovLight_mask.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645211\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f6c58556-1719-4fc2-a837-2a6a6ccba4cd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_mask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_mask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=485&amp;height=485 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h3 id=\"AOVLight-LightFiltersandPxrAovLight\">Light Filters and PxrAovLight</h3><p>Because PxrAovLight is a &quot;light&quot;, we can add a light filters to modify the output AOV.  In this example, the <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661767\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrIntMultLightFilter</a> is attached to PxrAovLight.  The Light Filter is only linked to the tree trunk, resulting in a gray value for the tree trunk mask.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/image2019-1-4_10-47-13.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138709&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=241\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645211/image2019-1-4_10-47-13.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138709&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"412\" data-width=\"1160\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645243\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image2019-1-4_10-47-13.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645211\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5052ff46-baf1-49db-ad0a-c9182c4bbda7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/image2019-1-4_10-47-13.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138709&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1160&amp;height=412 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/image2019-1-4_10-47-13.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138709&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=241 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"485\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=485&amp;height=485\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645211/aovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645231\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"aovLight_primary.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645211\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"83b6ac96-f26b-405d-95d7-ffa57c315904\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_primary.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=485&amp;height=485 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"485\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_filteredMask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=485&amp;height=485\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645211/aovLight_filteredMask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645237\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"aovLight_filteredMask.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645211\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"2acd8ee0-83c5-45f8-a4b1-873c3e05bcf9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_filteredMask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645211/aovLight_filteredMask.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433138498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=485&amp;height=485 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
